com.tumblr.backboard.imitator

Class SpringImitator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tumblr.backboard.imitator.Imitator
      • com.tumblr.backboard.imitator.SpringImitator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SpringListener

    public class SpringImitator
extends Imitator
implements SpringListener
    Allows a Spring to imitate another Spring.

    The default implementation sets the end value of the attached Spring to be the same as the current value of the couple it is imitating.

    Created by ericleong on 5/16/14.
